reviews.review_text:
Monaural Monophonic. 

Great show in up state New York. It would be nice to have this one in stereo from the board...this show is rockin'. 

The Dead with intro's, verses, choruses bridges, and refrains and endings. Rock'n the House. Keith sounds great...the whole show sounds great in MONO...this one is mind over matter, if you don't mind, it don't matter. Still a great show, the boys are in command. I will see how this one sounds in my ROXIO Easy Media Creator 9 when I enhance it, and make it stereo, and see what else I can tweak out of it. Thanks for the love.
